metadata.title: Outsidepride Pentas White Garden Flower Container Plant - 25 Seeds
features: If you are looking for beautiful, bright white, star-shaped flowers then look no further than this new Pentas hybrid seed.
These white pentas flowers grows as a perennial in USDA zones 9 - 11 only reaching 12 inches tall.
Ideal in a hot, sunny location, Pentas will grow into 12 inch tall mounds of brilliant white flowers.
Very striking in the garden or as a container plant. Its hybrid genetics ensures uniformity of plant habit and bloom time, and less need for growth regulators.
Sow 4 - 5 seeds per plant to begin growing these white pentas flowers.
